'''塞浦路斯－俄羅斯關係'''，是指[[俄羅斯聯邦|俄羅斯聯邦]]和[[塞浦路斯共和國|塞浦路斯共和國]]（而非[[北塞浦路斯土耳其共和國|北塞浦路斯土耳其共和國]]）之間的雙邊關係。[[蘇聯|蘇聯]]與塞浦路斯於1960年8月18日建交，而兩國之間的合作在蘇聯衰落及後來解體後有所增加。塞浦路斯在[[莫斯科|莫斯科]]設有[[大使館|大使館]]，俄羅斯亦於塞浦路斯首都[[尼科西亞|尼科西亞]]設有大使館。

蘇聯在塞浦路斯於1960年8月16日從[[英國|英國]]獨立兩日後建交；蘇聯解體後，塞浦路斯於1992年4月7日承認俄羅斯聯邦為蘇聯的主要繼承國<ref name="mid190508">{{ru icon}} {{cite web|url=http://www.mid.ru/ns-reuro.nsf/348bd0da1d5a7185432569e700419c7a/627e4168ead53d3cc325744e002f98da?OpenDocument|title=Российско-кипрские отношения|date=19 May 2008|publisher=[[Russian_Ministry_of_Foreign_Affairs|Russian Ministry of Foreign Affairs]]|accessdate=2009-03-31|archive-date=2011-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110615053040/http://www.mid.ru/ns-reuro.nsf/348bd0da1d5a7185432569e700419c7a/627e4168ead53d3cc325744e002f98da?OpenDocument|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 經貿關係 ==
塞浦路斯是俄羅斯的第三大外國投資者，但其實大多數來自塞浦路斯的外國直接投資者是為了在俄羅斯避稅或逃避法律責任<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.russiatoday.ru/Business/2009-04-23/Cyprus_comes_in_from_the_cold_as_tax_havens_feel_the_heat.html |title=Cyprus comes in from the cold as tax havens feel the heat |date=23 April 2009 |publisher=[[Russia_Today|Russia Today]] |accessdate=2009-04-23 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20120909153402/http://www.russiatoday.ru/Business/2009-04-23/Cyprus_comes_in_from_the_cold_as_tax_havens_feel_the_heat.html |archive-date=2012-09-09 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。塞浦路斯與俄羅斯其他地區（如[[韃靼斯坦共和國|韃靼斯坦共和國]]、[[聖彼得堡|聖彼得堡]]、[[克拉斯諾達爾邊疆區|克拉斯諾達爾邊疆區]]等）的經貿合作亦在穩步增長<ref name=noeng>{{cite web|title=Relations between Russia and Cyprus|url=http://www.cyprus.mid.ru/en/ru_cy.htm|publisher=Russian Embassy in the Republic of Cyprus|accessdate=2014-07-17|archive-url=https://archive.is/20130706085611/http://www.cyprus.mid.ru/en/ru_cy.htm|archive-date=2013-07-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>；於2005年3月22日，韃靼斯坦共和國經貿合作部與塞浦路斯商務、工業及旅遊部的簽署[[合作備忘錄|合作備忘錄]]<ref name=noeng />。於2013年3月，[[歐盟|歐盟]]單方面決定向塞浦路斯的銀行賬戶徵收一筆資金；根據俄罗斯以前與歐盟的談判，俄羅斯預計會增加向塞浦路斯批出的貸款，但預料歐盟上述的決定將嚴重打壓俄羅斯在塞浦路斯的資產，以致影響俄罗斯向塞浦路斯借貸的決定<ref>L. Kelly and A. Anishchuk (March 2013). [http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/03/18/us-russia-cyprus-idUSBRE92H0D920130318 Russia wants future involvement on Cyprus after "dangerous" levy] {{Wayback|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/03/18/us-russia-cyprus-idUSBRE92H0D920130318 |date=20150924180126 }} Reuters. Retrieved 2013-03-18.</ref>。

== 軍事關係 == 
1997年1月，塞浦路斯簽署協議，和俄國一所軍火商購買了40枚[[S-300導彈|S-300導彈]]，價值2億美元<ref name="bulletin">{{cite journal|last=Barletta|first=Michael|date=November 1998|title=Cyprus: Mediterranean countdown|journal=Bulletin of the Atomic Scientists|publisher=Educational Foundation for Nuclear Science, Inc.|volume=54|issue=6|pages=12–14|issn=00963402|url=http://books.google.com/?id=sgsAAAAAMBAJ|accessdate=2009-04-01}}</ref><ref name="essay"/>，造成與土耳其關係緊張，更威脅停止向塞浦路斯發送貨品，更指不排除採取軍事行動<ref name="essay">{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/1998/07/02/opinion/essay-primakov-in-cyprus.html|title=Essay; Primakov in Cyprus|last=Safire|first=Williams|date=2 July 1998|publisher=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]]|accessdate=2009-03-31|archive-date=2020-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115000144/https://www.nytimes.com/1998/07/02/opinion/essay-primakov-in-cyprus.html}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=Hannay|first=David|title=Cyprus: the Search for a Solution|publisher=I.B.Tauris|location=[[London|London]]; [[New_York|New York]]|year=2005|pages=70|chapter=1997: Missiles and Missed Opportunities|isbn=1-85043-665-7|accessdate=2009-04-01}}</ref><ref name="nyt290498">{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/1998/04/29/world/greek-cypriots-to-get-missiles-from-russians.html|title=Greek Cypriots To Get Missiles From Russians|last=Gordon|first=Michael R.|date=29 April 1998|publisher=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]]|accessdate=2009-03-31|archive-date=2020-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120094207/https://www.nytimes.com/1998/04/29/world/greek-cypriots-to-get-missiles-from-russians.html}}</ref>。[[俄羅斯外交部|俄羅斯外交部]]發言人表示，這筆交易純粹是商業基礎考慮，又指俄羅斯曾建議塞浦路斯停火<ref name="nyt290498"/；俄羅斯外長又指該批導彈是「防禦性武器」<ref name="nyt290498"/><ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/world/monitoring/57313.stm|title=Russia to honour missile contract with Cyprus — Primakov|date=16 February 1998|publisher=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|accessdate=2009-03-31|archive-date=2019-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191211171144/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/world/monitoring/57313.stm}}</ref>。但是，由於土耳其一直反對導彈，塞浦路斯從來沒有部署該批導彈，其後更把該批導彈轉運到[[希臘|希臘]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Cyprus transfers controversial S300 missiles to Greece |url=http://english.people.com.cn/90001/90777/6323968.html |accessdate=2014-07-17 |newspaper=People's Daily Online |date=2007-12-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071223133706/http://english.people.com.cn/90001/90777/6323968.html |archivedate=2007-12-23 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

